{"tha-ap233:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap233:0.2":"Udakasanavagga ","tha-ap233:0.3":"Udakasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap233:1.1":"“Aramadvara nikkhamma, ","tha-ap233:1.2":"phalakam santharim aham; ","tha-ap233:1.3":"Udakanca upatthasim, ","tha-ap233:1.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","tha-ap233:2.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap233:2.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap233:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap233:2.4":"asane codake phalam. ","tha-ap233:3.1":"Ito pannarase kappe, ","tha-ap233:3.2":"abhisamasamavhayo; ","tha-ap233:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap233:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap233:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap233:4.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap233:4.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap233:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap233:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma udakasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap233:6.1":"Udakasanadayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}